data.description: Back to Active because buyer dropped out! You've gotta see this spacious and updated single level 2 bedroom 2 bath condo with open floor plan and attached 2 car garage. Ceramic plank tile throughout the kitchen, living areas and bathrooms with carpet in the bedrooms. The huge primary bedroom has double closets and dual sinks in the ensuite bathroom. The kitchen features granite countertops, a breakfast bar with a view of the living room and stainless steel appliances. The HOA is priced very low and the unit is directly across from the large community pool and ramada.
